{"tid":2496753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中大保衛戰四人被控暴動開審 控方開案陳詞指從被告的服飾及被追捕時逃走反抗 肯定他們有參與暴動","createTime":"2021-04-20T04:42:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T05:03:31.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cc362484748aeaa1efed2343b1d24d14d4aab860","tid":2496753,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:42:07.000Z","msg":"前年11月中大衝突，四名大專生被控暴動等罪名，案件在區域法院開審，四人否認控罪。控方開案陳詞指，從被告的服飾及被追捕時逃走反抗，肯定他們有參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n三男一女被告抵達區域法院出席聆訊，四人否認所有控罪。<br />\n<br />\n控方在開案陳詞指，警方在前年11月12日駐守在中大二號橋，避免社會秩序再度受損，在場人士懷有共同目的，就是阻礙警方執行職務。當日下午在場集結人士增至過百人，三時許開始有人向警方防線投擲汽油彈、磚頭及雜物，非法集結演變成暴動。<br />\n<br />\n警方曾向群眾展示黑旗及橙旗，以揚聲器警告現場人士立即散去，但在場人士沒有理會，並向警方防線推進，警方之後採取拘捕行動，集結人士隨即逃跑，警員在環迴東路近物業管理處以及網球場等多處先後拘捕四名被告。<br />\n<br />\n控方指，從四人服飾看到他們戴上防毒面具、面罩等，加上警員追捕時逃走反抗，肯定他們有參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n4人被控一項暴動罪，指他們於前年11月12日在中大二號橋及環迴東路一帶，與其他不知名人士參與暴動，其中三人同時因為戴有護目鏡及防毒面具，被控於非法集會內蒙面；一人涉嫌攜帶可發出雷射光束的裝置，被控在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=431749\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D431749&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuIsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=26f7514e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D431749&h=2295ee27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=431749</a>"},{"pid":"242a686a28ed6c1001704628cecbfd103ecf5f3d","tid":2496753,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:43:21.000Z","msg":"又係衣著<br />\n咁睇有啲唔樂觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39723db73a6167c815e654b30b6f76a8ca4fad53","tid":2496753,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd957831d91e24a6eae0f285f3ff0441f39cce9","tid":2496753,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71e88ac51b224b24479f26227c349ec71c6c836","tid":2496753,"uid":275243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T05:01:01.000Z","msg":"呢單真係近乎斷正咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39af79c1827345b0488039682050de6da1dc8e1b","tid":2496753,"uid":146351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T05:03:31.000Z","msg":"斷到正一正"}]}